(2, 'Why do we use it?', '<div class=\"item_slide_show clearfix\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-rendering: geometricprecision; width: 900px; max-width: 100%; overflow: hidden; clear: both; color: #222222; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; position: relative;\">\r\n<div class=\"desc_cation\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 10px 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-rendering: geometricprecision; clear: both; max-width: 650px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 17px; line-height: 23px; background: transparent !important; float: none !important;\">\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; text-rendering: geometricprecision; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: 23px !important; margin: 0px !important 0px !important 15px 0px !important;\">Sau khi đ&egrave; bẹp Campuchia 4-0 tr&ecirc;n s&acirc;n Rizal Memorial (Manila), c&aacute;c cầu thủ Việt Nam đến khu kh&aacute;n đ&agrave;i d&agrave;nh cho CĐV đội nh&agrave; để chung vui. Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; lần đầu ti&ecirc;n sau 10 năm, Việt Nam v&agrave;o chung kết SEA Games.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\" />HLV Park Hang-seo sau đ&oacute; y&ecirc;u cầu c&aacute;c học tr&ograve; nhanh ch&oacute;ng v&agrave;o ph&ograve;ng thay đồ để nghỉ ngơi.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item_slide_show clearfix\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-rendering: geometricprecision; width: 900px; max-width: 100%; overflow: hidden; clear: both; color: #222222; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; position: relative;\">\r\n<div class=\"block_thumb_slide_show_ima